### Upload Blog Images
POST http://localhost:3000/blog/upload-images
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="images"; filename="image1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/image1.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

###

### Create Blog Post with Markdown (Simple Example)
POST http://localhost:3000/blog
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

{
  "author": "John Doe",
  "writingDate": "2025-11-09T10:00:00.000Z",
  "active": false,
  "translations": [
    {
      "language": "en",
      "title": "My First Markdown Blog Post",
      "markdownContent": "# Welcome to My Blog\n\nThis is my first blog post using **Markdown**!\n\n## Why Markdown?\n\n- Easy to write\n- Easy to read\n- Portable\n\n### Adding Images\n\nYou can add images directly in the text:\n\n![Example Image](https://your-minio-url.com/blog/example.jpg)\n\n### Code Snippets\n\n```javascript\nconst hello = 'world';\nconsole.log(hello);\n```\n\n> This is a quote\n\nVisit [our website](https://example.com) for more!"
    },
    {
      "language": "de",
      "title": "Mein erster Markdown-Blog-Beitrag",
      "markdownContent": "# Willkommen in meinem Blog\n\nDies ist mein erster Blog-Beitrag mit **Markdown**!\n\n## Warum Markdown?\n\n- Einfach zu schreiben\n- Einfach zu lesen\n- Portabel\n\n### Bilder hinzufügen\n\nSie können Bilder direkt im Text hinzufügen:\n\n![Beispielbild](https://your-minio-url.com/blog/example.jpg)"
    }
  ],
  "images": [
    {
      "url": "https://your-minio-url.com/blog/example.jpg",
      "altText": "Example image for blog post"
    }
  ],
  "links": [
    {
      "url": "https://example.com",
      "title": "Our Website"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Create Blog Post with Multiple Embedded Images
POST http://localhost:3000/blog
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

{
  "author": "Jane Smith",
  "writingDate": "2025-11-09T14:00:00.000Z",
  "active": false,
  "translations": [
    {
      "language": "en",
      "title": "Product Gallery: RevSticks 2025",
      "markdownContent": "# RevSticks 2025 Collection\n\nIntroducing our latest collection!\n\n## Classic Series\n\n![Classic Red](https://your-minio-url.com/blog/classic-red.jpg)\n\nThe **Classic Red** model features:\n- Premium grip\n- Lightweight design\n- Durable construction\n\n## Modern Series\n\n![Modern Blue](https://your-minio-url.com/blog/modern-blue.jpg)\n\nThe **Modern Blue** brings innovation:\n- Advanced materials\n- Ergonomic shape\n- Enhanced performance\n\n## Limited Edition\n\n![Gold Edition](https://your-minio-url.com/blog/gold-edition.jpg)\n\nOur exclusive **Gold Edition** is limited to 100 units!\n\n### Specifications\n\n| Model | Weight | Length | Price |\n|-------|--------|--------|-------|\n| Classic | 150g | 40cm | $99 |\n| Modern | 140g | 42cm | $129 |\n| Gold | 145g | 41cm | $299 |\n\n---\n\n*Pre-order now and get 10% off!*"
    }
  ],
  "images": [
    {
      "url": "https://your-minio-url.com/blog/classic-red.jpg",
      "altText": "Classic Red RevStick"
    },
    {
      "url": "https://your-minio-url.com/blog/modern-blue.jpg",
      "altText": "Modern Blue RevStick"
    },
    {
      "url": "https://your-minio-url.com/blog/gold-edition.jpg",
      "altText": "Gold Edition RevStick"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Get All Blog Posts (Public)
GET http://localhost:3000/blog

###

### Get Active Blog Posts Only (Public)
GET http://localhost:3000/blog?activeOnly=true

###

### Get Blog Posts in English (Public)
GET http://localhost:3000/blog?language=en

###

### Get Active Blog Posts in German (Public)
GET http://localhost:3000/blog?activeOnly=true&language=de

###

### Get Single Blog Post (Public)
GET http://localhost:3000/blog/YOUR_BLOG_ID_HERE

###

### Get Single Blog Post in French (Public)
GET http://localhost:3000/blog/YOUR_BLOG_ID_HERE?language=fr

###

### Update Blog Post
PATCH http://localhost:3000/blog/YOUR_BLOG_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

{
  "translations": [
    {
      "language": "en",
      "title": "Updated Title",
      "markdownContent": "# Updated Content\n\nThis is the **updated** markdown content.\n\n![New Image](https://your-minio-url.com/blog/new-image.jpg)"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Activate Blog Post
PATCH http://localhost:3000/blog/YOUR_BLOG_ID_HERE/activate
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

###

### Deactivate Blog Post
PATCH http://localhost:3000/blog/YOUR_BLOG_ID_HERE/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

###

### Delete Blog Post
DELETE http://localhost:3000/blog/YOUR_BLOG_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN
